  UUSSIINNGG XXDDIITTVVIIEEWW WWIITTHH DDIITTRROOFFFF

    You can use any ditroff output file with xxddiittvviieeww(1X11R5) although files
    which use the fonts appropriate to the fontMap will look more accurate on
    the screen. On servers which support scaled fonts, all requested font
    sizes will be accurately reflected on the screen; for servers which do not
    support scaled xxddiittvviieeww(1X11R5) will use the closest font from the same
    family.

